// Brokkr Dwarf Fighter/Thief
COPY ~grand_duke/cre/rqfith.cre~ ~override/rqfith.cre~
  SAY NAME1 ~Brokkr~
  SAY NAME2 ~Brokkr~
  SAY BIO ~I aint got time to talk to ye bout' me past!~
  SAY TIRED ~Bah! I'd rather be punchin' bums drunk than bein' worn out, ya hear?~
  SAY HURT ~Wounds be deep, ya pitiful fool! Help me, or I'll feed yer bones to the rats!~
  SAY TARGET_IMMUNE ~Bah! Not even a scratch! Gimme a better weapon, ye dolt!~
  SAY INVENTORY_FULL ~Dropped yer lousy trinkets. Git lost, or get a new bag!~
  SAY SPELL_DISRUPTED ~Hrrr! The spell's broken, blasted it!~
  SAY SET_A_TRAP ~Heh heh heh! Watch the stoopid look on their face when this trap bites 'em!~

